WEBVTT

00:00.640 --> 00:01.720
Xu'er is right

00:02.280 --> 00:03.120
To do great things

00:03.280 --> 00:04.120
One must have courage

00:04.600 --> 00:05.480
In this age of great contention

00:05.720 --> 00:06.600
Winds and clouds change constantly

00:07.280 --> 00:09.120
Being timid and dragging one's feet

00:09.400 --> 00:10.600
Will only lead to passivity

00:11.160 --> 00:11.720
Sheng'er

00:12.040 --> 00:14.400
It's good that you study governance daily

00:14.760 --> 00:15.560
But occasionally

00:15.560 --> 00:17.440
Also learn your second brother's boldness

00:18.120 --> 00:18.600
Yes

00:19.040 --> 00:20.760
Your son has learned
